{
  "texts": [
    "A chatbot is computer software that utilizes AI and natural-language processing to interpret queries and automate responses, emulating human interaction.",
    "In order to utilize a chatbot, an individual initiates a \"session\" by inputting a query, also known as a \"prompt,\" using simple and natural language.",
    "The user is generally a human being.",
    "The chatbot quickly generates a relevant natural-language \"response\" to the prompt, typically within 1 second.",
    "The ongoing interaction of ideas and responses persists throughout the session, resulting in a conversational dynamic akin to a dialogue between two individuals (3)."
  ]
}